    Ghc-Options: -Werror

  Build-Depends:    base >= 4.7,
                    distributed-process-test,
                    replicated-log

Test-Suite random
  Type:             exitcode-stdio-1.0
  Main-Is:          random.hs
  Default-Language: Haskell2010
  Hs-Source-Dirs:   tests

  Ghc-Options:      -Wall -threaded

  if flag(maintainer)
